short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A new tab chrome extension to create urgency

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Replaces your 'new-tab' page with a real-time counter showing your current age and the weeks of your life. Has dark-mode support!
----
Chrome extension that shows:
1. your age with a dramatical counter 
2. weeks of their life and how much of these you have already consumed
3. when people accomplished major milestones (compared to your age)

12-16 of successful people are selected at random on every new tab.
